# Electron + React Rules

Use existing AWKIT patterns:
- Electron main/preload code lives under `app/main`.
- Renderer UI uses React + TypeScript.
- Shared styles belong in existing CSS files, especially `app/renderer/styles/global.css`.
- Use existing components and state patterns before adding new abstractions.
- Keep preload IPC contracts stable.
- Never expose Node APIs directly to the renderer.
- Preserve `window.playwrightFlowStudio` as the renderer bridge contract.
